leg workout 
NOTE - ( train only quads ) 

Start with legs warm-up 
- dumble goblet squats - 4 × 20
- dumble lunges walk 3 set 
- leg press 4 × 15 
- single leg extension 3 × 15
- dumble front squats 3 × till failure 
- at the end 10 min incline walk ( speed - 6 , incline 15 )
.
